Interface Commentable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Comment, Concept, Instruction, Instrument, ResponseDomain, Study, SurveyProgram, TopicGroup

    public interface Commentable
    Interface defining functionality for all entity classes that support the notion of a comment and define the required functionality to support it.
